I love your shadowsocks client. Do you ever considered reimplement tun2socks in Scala? It may help to improve performance and make shadowsocks client easier to modify & improve for contributors. Also this app should be more than a lantern client, may be you should turn it into something like Surge for iOS, with both shadowsocks and HTTP Proxy over TLS(some call it HTTPS proxy) support. Thank you very much for all the work!
